1. *Ponuda* je bila dobra, ali nisam je prihvatio. (The offer was good, but I didn't accept it.)
2. *Ponudio* mi je posao pre nego što sam položio ispit. (He offered me a job before I passed the test.)
3. Ona će ti dati pravu *ponudu* kada bude spremna. (She will give you the right offer when she is ready.)
4. *Ponude* je bilo toliko da je bilo teško odabrati. (There were so many offers that it was hard to choose.)
5. Oni su često *ponudili* popuste kako bi privukli više kupaca. (They often offered discounts to attract more customers.)